FAQ

Q1&colon; Can i get sample first&quest;

A &colon;Yes &comma;the label sample is available if you would pay the friehgt &period;

In additon&comma;we can produce the sample with the custom design artwork printing if you pay the sample fee &period;

Q2&colon; Can i have sticker with graphic design and my logo printing &quest;

A &colon; Yes&comma;we are factory and accept OEM and ODM so we can make the sticker with your own design printing &period;

Q3&colon; How can i get price for the packaging i need fast &quest;

A &colon;Please send us email with specifications of the packaging you need &comma;including size&comma;shape&comma;material&comma;order quantity&comma;special printing request or design image&period;We will check the cost and quote you as soon as possible &period;

Q4&colon;Could you help with the design &quest;

A &colon; Yes&comma; our professional designers to help with simple information such as logo and some images&period;

Q5&colon;What's your production lead time&quest;

Around 6 to 15 days according to the order quantity and production details

Q6&colon;What is your minimum order quantity&quest;

Usually 5000 pieces but it is negotiable if there is many different size or design artwork

Q7&colon;What kind of files do you accept for printing&quest;

AI&comma; CDR&comma; PDF&comma; PSD&comma;EPS&comma; high resolution JPG or PNG
